【Optical Wired Mouse】This wired mouse features high-resolution optical technology, providing smooth and precise tracking that works on most surfaces. Its symmetrical design makes this mouse fit in any hands, ensuring comfort during work and study sessions.

【Wide Compatibility】EDJO wired keyboard and mouse combo is widely compatible with Windows XP/Vista/7/8/8.1/10, Mac and other operating systems, refer to Desktops, Chromebooks, PCs, Laptops, Computers and more, great for office work, daily use and various computing needs.

If you encounter any issues during usage, please feel free to contact the EDJO Customer Service Team via Amazon email for a quick response within 24 hours and access to technical support.
